name: Generic Backrooms reacreation num 130,057
description:
This is a simple little game made by me on unity as a side project to college.

Please don't expect too much from it.

It's features are: Randomly generated walls, a difficult to find exit and Flesh Orbs.

                                     Controls:
WASD to move 

Shift to sprint - but be careful, you can't do it forever...

Right click to zoom

and Left click to toggle your flashlight
